{"tid":827429,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"文段詩辭撚入","createTime":"2018-09-19T02:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T13:00:38.000Z","uid":209308,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b89cde10230540bdece684b3250a8d6218eb8051","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"人生得一知己，死有何憾？<br />\n以字寓情，以文載道。<br />\n與君相對對，尋興字行間<br />\n雅致如對酌，無酒勝有酒<br />\n眾笑我倆孤自賞，<br />\n與君作聯寄嘲言。<br />\n<br />\n字詞萬千，其意亦然<br />\n有以偏概全者，<br />\n有以言入罪者，<br />\n有以言會友者，<br />\n或然曰因字得詬，何以堅守言道？<br />\n無他，雖千萬人吾往矣<br />\n字之美，不能盡傳。<br />\n與君共相對，勝閱世間傳<br />\n<br />\n上面兩段野係我同一個朋友一人一段作出嚟既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時我地都中意作下短句/詩辭/對聯咁<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲一齊交流下<br />\n<br />\n拋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25424c8c4528f129739d75d6175b19642f585fd","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89cde10230540bdece684b3250a8d6218eb8051","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"人生得一知己，死有何憾？<br />\n以字寓情，以文載道。<br />\n與君相對對，尋興字行間<br />\n雅致如對酌，無酒勝有酒<br />\n眾笑我倆孤自賞，<br />\n與君作聯寄嘲言。<br />\n<br />\n字詞萬千，其意亦然<br />\n有以偏概全者，<br />\n有以言入罪者，<br />\n有以言會友者，<br />\n或然曰因字得詬，何以堅守言道？<br />\n無他，雖千萬人吾往矣<br />\n字之美，不能盡傳。<br />\n與君共相對，勝閱世間傳<br />\n<br />\n上面兩段野係我同一個朋友一人一段作出嚟既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時我地都中意作下短句/詩辭/對聯咁<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲一齊交流下<br />\n<br />\n拋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;磚&ldquo;"},{"pid":"3e188a64b7b95573256b425dd952d61b659a555e","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:25:41.000Z","msg":"《你》<br />\n<br />\n如水，滌靜了我的咶躁<br />\n如火，點燃了我的情緒<br />\n如風，吹走了我的憂鬱<br />\n如土，伴隨了我的腳步"},{"pid":"eab9017cd81d1484d1464938e05be850192b4a67","tid":827429,"uid":187076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"「一鄉二里共三夫子不識四書五經六義，竟敢教七八九子，十分大膽！」<br />\n<br />\n「十室九貧湊得八兩七錢六分五毫四厘，尚且三心二意，一等下流！」"},{"pid":"2a48421e15880f97c75b9b49d0c4d58e645f9f61","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"對聯<br />\n<br />\n屠盡六迴渺蒼生，忤逆天道墮修羅<br />\n鬧竭二界隱簾洞，歷遇劫禍修仙道<br />\n<br />\n好中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2948a95edcd52377490bbb4cea816d90400afb1","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"皎皎明月掛長空，瀝瀝夜星墜天河<br />\n柔柔皎月伴君眠，星河長空夢相見"},{"pid":"9b6566671c0c9eab227184599261bacd7437b36d","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"寂湖閒亭孤影酌<br />\n俗菊荒陌悠伐凌"},{"pid":"ead7974cc10755a26022338607cd1881c1264677","tid":827429,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eab9017cd81d1484d1464938e05be850192b4a67","tid":827429,"uid":187076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"「一鄉二里共三夫子不識四書五經六義，竟敢教七八九子，十分大膽！」<br />\n<br />\n「十室九貧湊得八兩七錢六分五毫四厘，尚且三心二意，一等下流！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"好工整咼"},{"pid":"10d8a16740a52be5a71abd1aa7c15531b88c8945","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"小亦無不可，<br />\n已事無不傲，<br />\n傳世無不同，<br />\n奇命無不獨。"},{"pid":"1a81650d708e5956ce437a616158cced70ec6cd1","tid":827429,"uid":27196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c5bb4bd61380f0b0a4cf821bcaa26f0e091f49","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a81650d708e5956ce437a616158cced70ec6cd1","tid":827429,"uid":27196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"Thz 巴"},{"pid":"9405c340bd4b183eedf99e51d594f034b7f2fcae","tid":827429,"uid":95264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"以文載道嘅「文」唔係解「文字」嘅文,如果想對得更工整可以話「以詩寄情,以文載道」"},{"pid":"21c977e10adc1c7eb1f01856a8c0bb6c7aea6519","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"有排我同個朋友好中意中國有嘻哈個Gai<br />\n<br />\n用左佢啲歌嚟改辭/Rap詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n虎山一望無前 覆手逆轉坤乾<br />\n老子頭頂藍天 口中吞雲吐煙<br />\n厭與世俗周旋 為那碎銀幾錢<br />\n無懼虎山照行 吾道苦行修僧<br />\n清醒尚有幾人 鶴樓目空浮雲<br />\n江湖流水孰真 社會超脫紅塵<br />\n<br />\n或論世道險惡 眾人虛榮作樂 <br />\n沉醉不願醒覺 我有我隱居五岳<br />\n即使把酒當歌 難敵去日苦多 <br />\n我釃酒臨江 敢問人生幾何<br />\n有人見高拜見低踩<br />\n難阻我除妖魔攘鬼怪<br />\n既然世不與我念 何妨鳴金鞘劍 做個悠然周延"},{"pid":"90e00ce1ffe999eb16ab0cf2cf8bafd9232930a8","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9405c340bd4b183eedf99e51d594f034b7f2fcae","tid":827429,"uid":95264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"以文載道嘅「文」唔係解「文字」嘅文,如果想對得更工整可以話「以詩寄情,以文載道」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"thz 巴打 原來如此 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfb051e581e988f1c6941da27f3b9368e0f72e3","tid":827429,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"你哋兩個真係好friend"},{"pid":"5c99d2d1fdb28889309505688d03a837d0936b1b","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n《緣》<br />\n人海中相遇而交，是緣。<br />\n凡俗中相背而去，是緣。<br />\n聚合散離。<br />\n緣起緣落。<br />\n萬般，皆是緣。<br />\n留不住，帶不走，何不淡然放手。<br />\n總會來，終失去，何不笑着面對。<br />\n<br />\n朋友<br />\n《緣》<br />\n事無常，心會變<br />\n緣易盡，念不亡<br />\n又有多少人能珍惜垂手可得的緣<br />\n錯過，恨過，不如定格身邊的人<br />\n一期，一會<br />\n一刻，一輩<br />\n半生緣，一生完"},{"pid":"abd6eacc2adb4f1fedce2297c2605aceb2d4394e","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfb051e581e988f1c6941da27f3b9368e0f72e3","tid":827429,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"你哋兩個真係好friend"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"係啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊時中學中史/econ堂成日唔聽書作野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地又係一齊讀文學科既<br />\n<br />\n中四開始已經有計劃一齊寫一本小說，不過我地兩個打文都打得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e92a2bb2b83c2191ab9360e7d81fb9e01611c6f","tid":827429,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59954685d2c1c3cc80ae69360528e3ce4613989c","tid":827429,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e92a2bb2b83c2191ab9360e7d81fb9e01611c6f","tid":827429,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"作乜？"},{"